Happy st. patrick's day, all!
Nick and I decided to make our adventure today to an party at club arcadia.
And although we look like monkeys... we're actually doing a jig, haha.
The music does keep cutting out, but from the bits and pieces that I do hear, it's some sort of irish music (obviously).  I just muted it and put on Justin Timberlake instead.

XXOO Leah

Today we lurked around Nexus Prime.  It was pretty goddamn rad if I do say so myself.
Anyway... nick started a blog too about our *GREAT ADVENTURES* over at http://sl.citytrafficpuzzle.net/ so go check that out if this gets too boring or something.
So when we got there we flew up to the top of the city and struggled until we realized that we could've taken the elevator.  And then we were exploring and came upon this turquoise... tunnel?  I guess you could call it that.  But it was a series of tunnels, pretty much a maze so we had to stop for a photo op and take pictures posing.

XXOO Leah.
